                        </div>
                        <p>Wealth planning, financial restructuring, business case evaluation and adaptation, client segmentation and go-to-market strategy, new products & trends identification, structuring and launch, adapted marketing and marketing tools; business network streamlining and optimization.</p>
                        <p>To enable you to invest successfully, we want to record and understand all aspects of your situation and your goals by means of a strategy discussion. During this interview, your investor profile will also be assessed on the basis of your willingness to take risks and your risk capacity. Our consultants proceed in a structured manner. A precisely defined advisory process creates the prerequisite for defining a tailor-made investment solution for you. During regular update meetings, the investment solution is reviewed, taking into account any changes in the personal situation, goals and market developments, and adjustments are made if necessary.</p>
                        <h3>Systematic analysis</h3>
                        <p>Our experts monitor worldwide market developments on a daily basis and analyse developments in the financial markets and in companies. Based on these findings, they develop a clear position and assessment of markets and asset classes that are unique to DFC. Depending on the investment solution, this knowledge is implemented directly for you when investing or you receive appropriate investment recommendations in order to be able to react to market developments and take advantage of market opportunities.</p>
                        <h3>Appropriate strategy</h3>
                        <p>Investors' needs and objectives are very individual. One can and wants to take more risks in order to generate a higher return, the other prefers to invest his money safely and in a balanced manner. The following questions need to be answered when choosing the most suitable investment strategy:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>What are your long-term financial goals and framework conditions?</li>
                            <li>What are your return expectations?</li>
                            <li>More importantly what fluctuation risks are you prepared to bear?</li>
