                        <p>With structured financing, we offer you a medium-term loan instrument for the realisation of strategic project financing. This is a framework financing consisting of one or more fixed advances. You can use a fixed advance both to finance a share deal and to purchase assets (asset deal, e.g. land, buildings, machinery, etc.) in the event of a succession arrangement, a management buy-out (MBO) or a leveraged buy-out (LBO). We procure the necessary capital for you and impart our know-how in structuring and optimising your transactions.</p>
