                        <p>Our humble objectives, as we embark on this landmark initiate, is to unreservedly support the vision of UNFCC Paris Accord objectives by replacing diesel and coal generation through clean and affordable electricity and making the world a better place.</p>
                        <p>We have gradually moved towards reducing electricity cost by replacing other expensive alternatives and carved the path to provide a strategic international platform for industry leaders, international investors and developers in achieving the world objectives towards the Green Energy initiatives. Consciously contributing towards the development of the program, DFC will endeavor to ensure our focus for the improvement and livelihood of the rural population with significant conservation of water evaporation and achieve the creation of better livelihoods and increase of income of the citizens where we operate. As we reap our energy requirements, DFC will equally ensure emphasis on preservation of biodiversity for the future. Our extended program construct will also ensure direct results on new creation of clusters of activities in Agriculture, Aquaculture and Tourism within the jurisdictions in supporting and complimenting new fields of work force.</p>
                        <p>DFC is constantly expanding in addition to various services in the planning and consultancy, we offer services in the field of technical management and mobile module measurements. Today you will find renewable energy solutions and services for systems of all sizes for residential as well as commercial and Industrial, as well as self-consumption solutions, planning and development of power plants in the megawatt range in open spaces and extensive services to safeguard income and asset optimization. Not only the goal of a sustainable future is critical for us as a company, and the road is important. So we exert ourselves on a daily basis, to close cycles to conserve resources and make so daily responsible decisions. We understand each other and our work as a building block of the energy transition.</p>
