                        </div>
                        <p>We aspire to be one of the largest real estate private equity firms in the world with $40 billion USD of assets under management. We operate around the globe with investments and people in Africa, North America, Europe, Asia and South America. We seek to generate attractive risk-adjusted returns for our investors across cycles and over the long term. Our Real Estate platform encompasses investments across the risk spectrum from opportunistic to core+ to debt.</p>
                        <p>We seek to acquire high quality investments at discounts to replacement cost. We then improve the properties through hands-on management and targeted value-add initiatives. Our efforts result in solid returns for clients, partners, investors and strong economic assets for communities. DFC’s real estate portfolio includes office, retail, hotel, industrial and residential properties. </p>
                        <p>A flexible mix of conditions and a comprehensive range of products and services for your real estate project.</p>
                        <ul>
